{"tid":1564971,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［法治薄弱］被剝奪提出訴訟的權利 維護私隱也做不到","createTime":"2019-09-13T03:24:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T04:29:11.000Z","uid":82224,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9abe2b1694c714bce6549d1c274d680c67bbb395","tid":1564971,"uid":82224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T03:24:51.000Z","msg":"彭指，現時K對手令詳情一無所知，包括哪位裁判官發出也不知道，被剝奪《基本法》第35條保障的提出訴訟權利，連踏出維護私隱的第一步也做不到。他又認為本案非學術討論，法庭應保障K的私隱，難保警方不會重施故技索取K的其他資料，或從其他醫生索取K的醫療資訊。<br />\n<br />\n彭續說根據醫院回信，警方索取K的醫療報告時，只稱想了解K為何受傷，並未表明懷疑有甚麼罪行發生；惟按照法例，只有在懷疑發生罪案的情況下才可申請法庭手令協助調查。<br />\n<br />\n代表警方的資深大律師郭莎樂回應說，認同K有權提起訴訟維護權益，但是次司法覆核不是正確程序。因為警方已經執行手令取得所需資料，根據案例不能再向發出手令的裁判官申請撤銷，已經太遲，正確做法是針對侵犯私隱，發起民事訴訟或司法覆核。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">法治基礎咁薄弱 炒撚晒班裁判官啦！</span></span>"},{"pid":"a6e0d7a2b2f72bb2edb16ed960589e732cb7fd1c","tid":1564971,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T03:25:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"96fef1670fbafb5c9a15d9da1f1eb72ba83e0d08","tid":1564971,"uid":25185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T03:26:59.000Z","msg":"【 突發】和理塞 商場篇 終於出爐!922第一彈約定你<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1563867\" target=\"_bla